Class USteamBit

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.u004.steamid.utils.USteamBit

  • public final class USteamBit
extends Object
    A Steam Id bits utility.

    USteamBit is the utility class for all offsets and masks of the Steam Id bit vector.
